box.text: (I actually don't think steppers are calibrated since the x/y size of the machine is constant. They are mapped to the full step/half step values at the top of the patch.)

INSTRUCTIONS

Move drawing machine pen to origin. Both motors should be near each other, and pen should be in that same corner of the machine.

Attach power supply to drawing machine

Connect USB from drawing machine to computer

Open this max patch

Click the "READY" toggle

Calibrate the machine if necessary

Open Processing Sketch

Load Image

After image is displayed, click "Image Mode" button to preview drawing.

If it needs adjustment, fiddle with the controls and click "REGENERATE"

Once satisfied, in Max patch, click "ready" check box, and then "begin" button
